Vendored for spec 011 (Warm-Modern Facelift) per FR-003.

NOTE: This directory ships the LICENSE marker. The actual subsetted WOFF2 file
(Latin-1 + numerals subset, variable weight 400-700) MUST be placed at
inter-variable.woff2 by an operator with network access. Until then, the
@font-face declaration in tokens.css will fail to fetch and the browser will
fall back to system-ui sans. This is documented as a deferred-asset condition
in specs/011-warm-modern-facelift/implementation-notes.md.
